{"tid":520581,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[激似] 王菀芝 唱 港版東京喰種","createTime":"2018-01-05T14:50:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T04:26:55.000Z","uid":28823,"like":29,"dislike":344,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"03aa30795d727920e7bf1e0aca66c14c2e142132","tid":520581,"uid":28823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T14:50:39.000Z","msg":"今獲真係樂壇有救，香港樂壇復活啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說我坐免費巴士返公司，聽到司機開收音機，電台播歌...<br />\n聽到有隻歌，屌啦星點解咁撚好聽，仲有種好熟悉既味道...?<br />\n第一次聽，已經心中跟住隻歌一齊唱，估唔到近代粵語仲有咁正既歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住問朋友 : 「有隻歌好正，歌詞唔記得，有&quot;花&quot;+&quot;雨&quot;」<br />\n然後我朋友靠依兩隻&quot;單字&quot;真係搵到隻歌( PS : 花字出得一次，無雨字，唔明點解佢可以搵番隻歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n跟住兩個share耳機一齊聽，好撚好聽，仆街，咁似東京喰種OP ????<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RC6edqo5wH8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRC6edqo5wH8&d=3G27iXfkleI%2BSqobtAB8jv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=6203358c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RC6edqo5wH8</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uMeR2W19wT0&amp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuMeR2W19wT0%26&d=3G27iXfkleI%2BSqobtAB8jv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=10d67b0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uMeR2W19wT0&amp;</a><br />\n<br />\n覺得唔似都唔緊要，因為難得有近代香港歌，唔係愛情歌，好感動..<br />\n個BGM同唱法好似東京喰種，BGM好柔和再有鼓聲高潮...<br />\n唱法就唱到好似就斷氣死咁，有種淒美感，好似東京喰種OP咁渣實春袋唱..<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個死人PV畫面又好撚恐怖，唔知搞乜，好似東京喰種ED食人肉咁...<br />\n歌詞仲要好似日本咁，好似講人生觀好似好文藝好隱世好深奧咁，但你睇完歌詞又不能完全唔明填詞人想帶出咩道理)<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「完全未怕冷，寒冰之山綻放的花，紅泛著兩眼，淚水總可力抗風沙<br />\n遊歷大世界能一登天際那梯階，尋覓在某處能千秋不變老的街<br />\n未曾折服自信可再飛起，那怕給我天氣漸變壞<br />\n塵落在世界，浮生一刻踏破鐘擺」<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n你老未，好高質呀，仲好洗腦，依四句可以係條街/公司狂LOOP住狂出口，就好似馬國明套 &quot; 誰願見死不救像石頭&quot;(依句野仲要高質過見死不夠石頭好多)<br />\n<br />\n聽完隻歌，我決定新年去旅行，去睇雪了，這首歌，給我內心打了強心針，為了「她」..."},{"pid":"d8922f95f64b750bf3faada85c300b3319c0585a","tid":520581,"uid":28823,"like":1,"dislike":42,"score":-41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T14:55:17.000Z","msg":"如果想比負皮果D，唔該拎耳機，由頭聽到尾啦隻歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20bacbd055f554998ee692dad7f462393eedb863","tid":520581,"uid":21456,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T15:00:33.000Z","msg":"未睇先負 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5484bded2206b4c00cfd86088e9c69655e2fd811","tid":520581,"uid":6327,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"quote":{"pid":"20bacbd055f554998ee692dad7f462393eedb863","tid":520581,"uid":21456,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T15:00:33.000Z","msg":"未睇先負 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T15:02:04.000Z","msg":"叫樓主去驗耳好能過"},{"pid":"e610f17134ad4c5dd9233b4708a29ac4daa68874","tid":520581,"uid":39181,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T15:04:06.000Z","msg":"唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a34635ef2c8c0d29dbb26f62309b10292d8ff1d6","tid":520581,"uid":28823,"like":0,"dislike":28,"score":-28,"quote":{"pid":"5484bded2206b4c00cfd86088e9c69655e2fd811","tid":520581,"uid":6327,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"quote":{"pid":"20bacbd055f554998ee692dad7f462393eedb863","tid":520581,"uid":21456,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T15:00:33.000Z","msg":"未睇先負 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T15:02:04.000Z","msg":"叫樓主去驗耳好能過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T15:04:46.000Z","msg":"屌啦星上次POST 蝴蝶圖想你地講係唔係東京喰種，點知負皮我<br />\n今次POST音樂，你地又GET唔撚到，點搞呀，認真D好唔好"},{"pid":"22d305f423d8c011a8b1b1439a0ea966028