d6d9b9136ddede3f673764820d3c","tid":520581,"uid":137978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T03:50:29.000Z","msg":"唔覺得似東京喰種喎<br />\n但佢首歌同mv都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29fd0952ec34cd0e661a4e3a7dcbc98a2fc9c761","tid":520581,"uid":117472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T04:06:48.000Z","msg":"負皮 比你fake左入黎<br />\n都唔撚似"},{"pid":"11512cfd6c3aa395c451a60b5c49275cd125ed80","tid":520581,"uid":34427,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T04:08:15.000Z","msg":"正皮係俾ivana<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43fd8747b0d6f12027dcf70a7430078043ea1e62","tid":520581,"uid":10976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T04:23:18.000Z","msg":"王菀之一向有做開呢類歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n該死的快樂的、我們他們、留白、雷電。等等等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47bf224b40d5b27098f38a43d64211ec331a98e3","tid":520581,"uid":10976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T04:25:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>王菀之一向有做開呢類歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n該死的快樂<del>的</del>、我們他們、留白、雷電 等等等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"972b00bc118340e49b9766b32f6fdb18830d2ae1","tid":520581,"uid":605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T04:50:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今獲真係樂壇有救，香港樂壇復活啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說我坐免費巴士返公司，聽到司機開收音機，電台播歌...<br />\n聽到有隻歌，屌啦星點解咁撚好聽，仲有種好熟悉既味道...?<br />\n第一次聽，已經心中跟住隻歌一齊唱，估唔到近代粵語仲有咁正既歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住問朋友 : 「有隻歌好正，歌詞唔記得，有&quot;花&quot;+&quot;雨&quot;」<br />\n然後我朋友靠依兩隻&quot;單字&quot;真係搵到隻歌( PS : 花字出得一次，無雨字，唔明點解佢可以搵番隻歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n跟住兩個share耳機一齊聽，好撚好聽，仆街，咁似東京喰種OP ????<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RC6edqo5wH8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRC6edqo5wH8&d=3G27iXfkleI%2BSqobtAB8jv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=6203358c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RC6edqo5wH8</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uMeR2W19wT0&amp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuMeR2W19wT0%26&d=3G27iXfkleI%2BSqobtAB8jv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=10d67b0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uMeR2W19wT0&amp;</a><br />\n<br />\n覺得唔似都唔緊要，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為難得有近代香港歌，唔係愛情歌</span></span>，好感動..<br />\n個BGM同唱法好似東京喰種，BGM好柔和再有鼓聲高潮...<br />\n唱法就唱到好似就斷氣死咁，有種淒美感，好似東京喰種OP咁渣實春袋唱..<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個死人PV畫面又好撚恐怖，唔知搞乜，好似東京喰種ED食人肉咁...<br />\n歌詞仲要好似日本咁，好似講人生觀好似好文藝好隱世好深奧咁，但你睇完歌詞又不能完全唔明填詞人想帶出咩道理)<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「完全未怕冷，寒冰之山綻放的花，紅泛著兩眼，淚水總可力抗風沙<br />\n遊歷大世界能一登天際那梯階，尋覓在某處能千秋不變老的街<br />\n未曾折服自信可再飛起，那怕給我天氣漸變壞<br />\n塵落在世界，浮生一刻踏破鐘擺」<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n你老未，好高質呀，仲好洗腦，依四句可以係條街/公司狂LOOP住狂出口，就好似馬國明套 &quot; 誰願見死不救像石頭&quot;(依句野仲要高質過見死不夠石頭好多)<br />\n<br />\n聽完隻歌，我決定新年去旅行，去睇雪了，這首歌，給我內心打了強心針，為了「她」...</blockquote><br />\n一睇就知你無聽本地歌<br />\n邊忽全部情歌？"},{"pid":"73fbd673ce185e9753aedeba3c51f368c51a6e37","tid":520581,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3c26323135026f7f94958a90b977c6a2ba0a707","tid":520581,"uid":91631,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T23:30:57.000Z","msg":"負左評先講<br />\n<br />\n邊間教會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T04:55:07.000Z","msg":"+1 樓主邊間教會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"