\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「完全未怕冷，寒冰之山綻放的花，紅泛著兩眼，淚水總可力抗風沙<br />\n遊歷大世界能一登天際那梯階，尋覓在某處能千秋不變老的街<br />\n未曾折服自信可再飛起，那怕給我天氣漸變壞<br />\n塵落在世界，浮生一刻踏破鐘擺」<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n你老未，好高質呀，仲好洗腦，依四句可以係條街/公司狂LOOP住狂出口，就好似馬國明套 &quot; 誰願見死不救像石頭&quot;(依句野仲要高質過見死不夠石頭好多)<br />\n<br />\n聽完隻歌，我決定新年去旅行，去睇雪了，這首歌，給我內心打了強心針，為了「她」...</blockquote><br />\n一睇就知你無聽本地歌<br />\n邊忽全部情歌？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:47:51.000Z","msg":"無話全部愛情歌，而係話大部份都係愛情歌，好撚悶，千篇一律.."},{"pid":"d61c659f8ae024e3f180cf8b84dc56f7117942d8","tid":520581,"uid":28823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73fbd673ce185e9753aedeba3c51f368c51a6e37","tid":520581,"uid":162783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3c26323135026f7f94958a90b977c6a2ba0a707","tid":520581,"uid":91631,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T23:30:57.000Z","msg":"負左評先講<br />\n<br />\n邊間教會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T04:55:07.000Z","msg":"+1 樓主邊間教會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  只可以講有一成似"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:48:14.000Z","msg":"完全唔明討論隻歌關教會咩事.."},{"pid":"046755365fec921dffe96f98f3093aecaa0f6d75","tid":520581,"uid":28823,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"fcdab1f89fe111b1de4a18bc2f29ede87006b36c","tid":520581,"uid":44298,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:08:12.000Z","msg":"之之首歌俾你搞到俾人反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T05:48:53.000Z","msg":"明明我係支持佢，係撐佢依隻歌，點解會比你地盲反，我真係推乜死乜..."},{"pid":"c7ace05f7140a0fc64fab7ed9f48f2c0ffa9c9fd","tid":520581,"uid":34427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T06:01:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>王菀之一向有做開呢類歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n該死的快樂的、我們他們、留白、雷電。等等等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"